'''Anne Gerety''' ([[July 3]], [[1920s#1926|1926]] &ndash; [[October 25]], [[2003]])<ref name="Prabook" /> played [[Beru Whitesun Lars/Legends|Beru Lars]] in the [[Star Wars (radio)|''Star Wars'' radio drama]]. She performed alongside her real-life husband [[Thomas Hill]], who played [[Owen Lars/Legends|Owen Lars]].<ref name="Gerety">{{WebCite|url=https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/262645559/anne-gerety|text=Anne Gerety|work=[[Wikipedia:Find a Grave|Find a Grave]]|archivedate=20240224034335}}</ref><ref name="Hill">{{WebCite|url=https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/36382523/thomas-newton-hill|text=Thomas Newton Hill Jr.|work=[[Wikipedia:Find a Grave|Find a Grave]]|date=2009-04-26|archivedate= 20210204133714}}</ref>

